77
00:09:40.498 --> 00:09:46.214
Du er gal, mand. Gal. Bare vent
til du ser min Yelp!-anmeldelse.


78
00:09:57.350 --> 00:10:02.312
Jeremy! Jeremy, vent!

79
00:10:02.395 --> 00:10:05.691
Hør her. Bare hør her!

80
00:10:05.774 --> 00:10:11.823
- Hvad var det?
